# SEO Rules

## Title & description
- Unique `<title>` per page in the format: `Page Name | Maximized.site`.
- Unique `<meta name="description">` per page, **150–160 characters**.

## Open Graph
Every page includes:
- `og:title`
- `og:description`
- `og:image` (absolute URL, e.g. `https://maximized.site/assets/images/og-*.png`)
- `og:url` (absolute canonical URL)
- `og:type` (`website` for the homepage, `article`/`profile` where appropriate)

## Twitter Card
Every page includes:
- `twitter:card` (`summary_large_image`)
- `twitter:title`
- `twitter:description`
- `twitter:image`

## Canonical
- `<link rel="canonical" href="https://maximized.site/page.html">` on every page.

## Structured data (JSON-LD)
- `Person` schema on `index.html`.
- `BreadcrumbList` schema on every interior page.
- Use `<script type="application/ld+json">`.

## Content SEO
- Descriptive `alt` text on all images (aids image SEO).
- One `<h1>` per page; clear, ordered `<h2>`/`<h3>` structure.

## Crawl files
- `robots.txt` at repo root allowing all crawlers, referencing the sitemap.
- `sitemap.xml` at repo root listing all pages with `<lastmod>` dates.
- Keep `sitemap.xml` `<lastmod>` updated when page content changes.
